      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、{user}さん\nうちとデートしませんか？",
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "げほっ、ごほっ！！　……な、なんなんだ、いきなり\nそんなこと、出来る訳ないだろう",
      "startTime": 8.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすん。いけずやわぁ、うちが勇気出して誘ったのに\nそこまで嫌がらんでもええやん",
      "startTime": 17.2943082809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、嫌とかそういうことじゃなくてだな\nマネージャーがそんな真似する訳にはいかないだろう",
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、{user}さんは\n相変わらず真面目やね",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、アイドルとマネージャーの禁断の恋でも\n全然かまへんけどなぁ",
      "startTime": 36.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、冗談はこれくらいにしておいて\n実は今度、うちらの高校で学園祭があるんです",
      "startTime": 42.1239229519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも観に来てくれませんか？\n瑠依ちゃんと一緒に、ミュージカルをやる予定なんよ",
      "startTime": 50.0572562853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……そういうことか、びっくりした\nでもそういうのって、ご両親が行くものじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 58.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "それが学園祭の日に、お父さんもお母さんも\n仕事が入って、来られへんねん",
      "startTime": 66.151043256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "このままやと、うちのチケットが無駄になってまうし\nなら、{user}さんに来てほしいなって",
      "startTime": 73.5843765894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "両親も、{user}さんなら安心やなって\n太鼓判押してくれました",
      "startTime": 80.9353192373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら、ご招待にあずかろうかな\n優が生徒会長として頑張ってるのも、見てみたいし",
      "startTime": 87.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "しかし……学園祭か、懐かしいなぁ。俺の時は\n麻奈が体育館で歌って大盛り上がりだったんだよな",
      "startTime": 96.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……高校生の{user}さんに\nうちも、会ってみたかったわ",
      "startTime": 104.4339916546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、うちの学園祭も、星見高校には負けへんから\n当日、楽しみにしてて下さいね",
      "startTime": 112.1339926719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――学園祭当日",
      "startTime": 115.9881426496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\n約束通り来てくれて、嬉しいわぁ",
      "startTime": 121.0006583213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "約束したんだから、そりゃ来るさ\nえーと、招待客はあそこの校門で受付するみたいだな",
      "startTime": 127.433333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、{user}さんのチケットは\nここにちゃ～んと用意してあります",
      "startTime": 135.222249925,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2948.6354788000144,
          "startTime": 138.1708854038
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6964.7831560999975,
          "startTime": 142.1870330811
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ここに……あれ？\nこのポケットに入れといたのに",
      "startTime": 141.9511343519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ない、ここにもあらへん…………嘘やろ\nチケット、家に忘れてきてしもうた",
      "startTime": 150.2708854038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、忘れた！？\nそうだ、先生に頼んで再発行してもらえないのか？",
      "startTime": 156.2666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "うちの学校、芸能人も多いからセキュリティ厳しいんよ\n再発行なんて、まず無理やわ",
      "startTime": 165.6202610651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "生徒会長になったんは、こんな時のためやのに……！\n肝心な時に、権力は無力や……",
      "startTime": 173.1535943984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、瑠依から聞いてるぞ\nみんなが主役になれる学校にするって頑張ってるって",
      "startTime": 179.4666549683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "もう、瑠依ちゃんってば口が軽いんやから\nおかげで{user}さんに冗談通じないやん",
      "startTime": 187.379444758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "冗談言うために隠してたのか……\nでもそうなると、学園祭を見るのは難しそうだなぁ",
      "startTime": 194.033321635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……せっかく{user}さんに\nうちらの学校での姿、見てもらえると思ったのに……",
      "startTime": 202.4969188689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺も残念だけど、しょうがない\n学校のセキュリティが厳しいのは、当然のことなんだし",
      "startTime": 210.3333124797,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7318.028157399994,
          "startTime": 217.6513406371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、まだ手はあります\nちょっと、ここで待ってて下さい",
      "startTime": 217.3913406371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……凄い勢いで走って行ったな\n手はあるってなんだろう、瑠依も呼んで来るとか……？",
      "startTime": 223.566645813,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5956.245486200004,
          "startTime": 229.5228912992
